{"name":"Animist Reading","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You spend 1 minute touching, playing with, or feeding an animal, object, or plant to learn a piece of information about an emotional event that occurred involving the target within the past week, determined by your GM. If you use @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-nature-archetypes.llguLGNyztcBDdbZ]{Animist Reading (1st)} on the same target multiple times, you can either concentrate on a single event to gain additional pieces of information about that event, or gain a piece of information about another emotional event in the applicable time frame. When the target has no further information to give, you receive a satisfying sense of closure. At 4th level, you can learn about an event that occurred within the last month; at 8th level, the last year; at 12th level, the last decade; at 16th level, the last century; at 18th level, the targetâ€™s history.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"animist-reading","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["divination","exploration","occult","primal"]},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"category":null,"actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Passive.webp","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.S5Ksms2yrM5iZX9n"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686060551410,"modifiedTime":1686072579803,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"lZvS9n4khMnAolkV"}
